rows.label: qst005802_msg0001
rows.name:
Well, we've arrived at the Isle
of Sleeping Remains, but...

rows.label: qst005802_msg0002
rows.name: Was there really a kingdom here?

rows.label: qst005802_msg0003
rows.name:
I can't see anything that
suggests there was...

rows.label: qst005802_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe monsters rampaged
and destroyed everything?

rows.label: qst005802_msg0005
rows.name: Hmm, in that case... We shall dig!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0007
rows.name:
Even if the buildings on the surface
are destroyed, their remains and
underground ruins are not so easily broken.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0009
rows.name:
Kubira, that's a bit of a stretch.
It would take too much time.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0010
rows.name:
It is an order from your
king. Begin at once!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0011
rows.name: He's not listening at all, mo...

rows.label: qst005802_msg0012
rows.name: Oh, well. We've come this far.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0013
rows.name: I'll stick with Kubira until the end.

rows.label: qst005802_msg0014
rows.name:
Once you take on a job,
you see it through!

rows.label: qst005802_msg0015
rows.name:
Is that another one of your
Salvager's Code things?

rows.label: qst005802_msg0016
rows.name:
Well, I guess I'll stick it out
with you 'til the bitter end.
